{"tid":1300352,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"考PADI潛水牌有冇咩好推介？","createTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T12:35:40.000Z","uid":238593,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6ff3ea795147459c438067f7a5fab5ba30a04c32","tid":1300352,"uid":238593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"諗住八月自己一個出東南亞考潛水牌 (毒L搵唔到伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n上網睇左好多菲律賓泰國日本印尼好多都包住宿來回機場接送個啲 大概$5000hkd成個Course 睇到眼花繚亂唔知點簡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打絲打有冇咩私心好介紹 我個Budget係 $5000樓下 當然唔包機票 同埋想治安好啲 (利申：絲打唔想比人食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"364248fb25af531a0d99c452e8db381c84292184","tid":1300352,"uid":102209,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:00:16.000Z","msg":"年頭去咗菲律賓Bohol考 個海真係超級靚又多嘢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剩係考好似3000幾港紙 唔敢搵好平嗰d 同埋教我個教練識廣東話<br />\n當地洗費勁平 我住先200幾蚊晚 獨立廁所 近沙灘<br />\n同埋都唔少台灣大陸女仔一個人黎學<br />\n<br />\n不過你一個女仔驚可能台灣綠島嗰d會啱你d"},{"pid":"a5ac6fa1880471c35a840ca03f03149e13805a0d","tid":1300352,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"我都想學，<br />\n但諗到一個人學完邊度搵個buddy返黎一齊潛<br />\n就無學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8f10fd1389b59841c895ea555b962f66bd77b7","tid":1300352,"uid":158422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ff3ea795147459c438067f7a5fab5ba30a04c32","tid":1300352,"uid":238593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"諗住八月自己一個出東南亞考潛水牌 (毒L搵唔到伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n上網睇左好多菲律賓泰國日本印尼好多都包住宿來回機場接送個啲 大概$5000hkd成個Course 睇到眼花繚亂唔知點簡好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問巴打絲打有冇咩私心好介紹 我個Budget係 $5000樓下 當然唔包機票 同埋想治安好啲 (利申：絲打唔想比人食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe433a0c6bb96979cca4dc07613bc43a3a79cc6","tid":1300352,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"八月中去墾丁考 可以一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421731f09f5f7cd9a0d9559c40beb5967dd431a4","tid":1300352,"uid":362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ac6fa1880471c35a840ca03f03149e13805a0d","tid":1300352,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"我都想學，<br />\n但諗到一個人學完邊度搵個buddy返黎一齊潛<br />\n就無學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"未必要buddy, 我有時去都係DM 一對一出去"},{"pid":"1b712a1016b20575fd10ce7005850e831cab7776","tid":1300352,"uid":362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5ac6fa1880471c35a840ca03f03149e13805a0d","tid":1300352,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"我都想學，<br />\n但諗到一個人學完邊度搵個buddy返黎一齊潛<br />\n就無學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"同埋我係香港學，教水的會都會一年出trip 一次"},{"pid":"d08b1d97fcbaf7e86cc404254d12069e2a04ee0c","tid":1300352,"uid":34788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"上個月係Bohol返嚟，機票潛水住宿加埋六千左右,不過係share房，單人房好似六千四<br />\n食同玩計埋tips就都係千幾，去左五日四夜。"},{"pid":"fcc5294b50e8feee97c15067f00e90f1187ec963","tid":13